---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Wie_Team from '../assets/images/wie-team.jpg'

import Instagram from '../assets/instagram.svg';
import LinkedIn from '../assets/linkedin.svg';
---

<Layout >
	<section class="bg-[url('../assets/images/hero-wie-2025.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat min-h-[95vh] flex items-center justify-center text-white">
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-10 font-heading-fam font-bold">
			<h1 class="text-6xl uppercase">leading the future together</h1>
			<h1 class="z-100 text-4xl">16th Annual IEEE WIE Wine and Cheese</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-col gap-2 mr-2">
			<img src={Instagram.src} width="30" height="30" alt="" class="invert brightness-0"/>
			<img src={LinkedIn.src} width="30" height="30" alt="" class="invert brightness-0"/>
		</div> 
	</section>
	<!-- <section class="bg-zinc-50 py-50 px-15">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5 border-2 border-dashed items-center">
			<div class="child1 text-xl space-y-5">
				<p>
					Just like you, we think that the future looks brighter when everyone is working together and contributing to build and innovate. This is why IEEE Women in Engineering (WIE) is the largest international professional organization dedicated to promoting women engineers and scientists. Our mission is to facilitate the global recruitment and retention of women in technical disciplines through affirmative action. IEEE WIE envisions a vibrant community of IEEE women, men and people from all over the gender spectrum collectively using their diverse talents and perspectives to accelerate progress toward a sustainable future with innovative technology.
				</p>
				<p>
					Locally, the IEEE WIE student branches at the University of Ottawa and Carleton University seek this brighter future by connecting students with industry leaders, like yourself, through events such as the annual Wine & Cheese. We have put together this event for sixteen years now, to benefit you in seeking the best candidates for internships, coops, and future coworkers
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="child2">
				<img src={Wie_Team.src} alt="">    
			</div>  
		</div>
	</section> -->

	<section id="welcome" class="bg-zinc-50 py-20 px-6">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-black/5 p-8 md:p-12">
			<div class="space-y-5">
				<p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500">Welcome</p>
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading-fam font-bold text-zinc-900">
				Building a stronger engineering community—together.
				</h2>

				<div class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-700 space-y-4">
				<p>
					IEEE Women in Engineering (WIE) supports and advances women and underrepresented groups in technical fields through community, mentorship, and professional opportunities.
				</p>
				<p>
					Locally, the University of Ottawa and Carleton University WIE student branches connect students and industry through events like our annual Wine &amp; Cheese—bringing together emerging talent and employers in a welcoming, high-energy setting.
				</p>
				</div>

				<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-zinc-700">
				<li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-400"></span>Meet standout students for co-ops, internships, and new grad roles</li>
				<li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-400"></span>Support an inclusive engineering community in Ottawa</li>
				<li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-400"></span>Build relationships with student leaders and faculty</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
				<img src={Wie_Team.src} alt="IEEE WIE team" class="h-full w-full object-cover"/>
			</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>